      "notes": [
        "mannage] This good English translation (whereof see many examples in Schmidt s. v.) is now, I think, quite lost, and we have returned to its French original, manège.—Ed."
      ]
    },
    "14": {
      "play": "end, riders dearly hired. But I, his brother, gain",
