    "62": {
      "play": "JAQUES: ’Tis a Greek invocation to call fools into a",
      "notes": [
        "to call fools into a circle] for the purpose of etymologically and linguistically investigating the meaning of 'Ducdame,' says MOBERLY, dryly."
