        "vnseasonably] Apparently through a mere oversight Steevens in his edition of 1793 inserted very before this word; thereupon the error curvetted unseasonably through the Variorums of 1803, 1813, 1821, and Singer’s first edition, until Knight cried holla to it.—ED."
