    "19": {
      "play": "TOUCHSTONE: No, truly, for the truest poetry is the most",
      "notes": []
    },
    "20": {
      "play": "feigning, and lovers are given to poetry, and what",
      "notes": []
    },
    "21": {
      "play": "they swear in poetry may be said as lovers they do",
